{"tid":1631964,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［對家戰線轉咗型！］宣布選戰任務正式上線，對準政權！！！要做文宣同起偽素人背景！！！","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:41:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T18:23:20.000Z","uid":287844,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5caa2c12edb34ea51a84f43157e6e51c7f6fdfb1","tid":1631964,"uid":287844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:41:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>我地淨係知選戰，對家好緊張，急到要Show hand出緊急法，所以請連登軍師俾意見，任何戰線只要有幫助，<br />\n敵人反對的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋就要擁護</strong></span></strong>[/size=5]<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">佢而家放風要延期/取消區選，就知佢而家嘅弱點係邊！ <br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n 為何區議會選舉這麼重要，急到要出緊急法？<br />\n<br />\n喺四百多席入面，如果我哋可以運用智慧，做文宣，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">盡全力攞八成議席 盡力囉！！！</span></span></strong>，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"> <br />\n區議會議席入面有<span style=\"font-size: large;\">一百幾票</span>選舉委員會的議席，加上現有的三百多席共有五百多席，</span></span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">大家要記得 600席就可以影響到提名特首人選</span></span></strong>， 只要立法會選舉功能組別做得好一些， 選特首在望， 但選戰充滿變數！！！<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n我哋要加選戰入主線任務！！！因為對方巳經不擇手段阻止區選，即係話係佢嘅弱點！！！</span></strong></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咁有咩可以做：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 連登鍵戰力量--<br />\n起偽政治素人底</span></span></strong>：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我哋需要知道邊個係保皇黨嘅人&bull;</span></span></strong><br />\n再係<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">11月24前做大量文宣</span></strong>，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">宣傳邊啲係偽素人！！連儂牆係我哋重要渠道接觸非同溫層！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 求連登精算師！分析區選人口比例策略</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咪睇少禮義廉，佢哋玩左好多年！！但我哋仲係新手，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連登軍師係時候出手喇！！小弟愚昧唔識...，但集各人智慧、攻其弱點！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>3. 手足，參選到嘅參選，投到嘅投票！！！</strong><br />\n</span></span><br />\n我哋巳經有2000個手足被捕，我地唔可以再失更多，哩場運動最重要嘅係我哋嘅手足！！！ 唔準再受傷，與其落場損兵折將，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">我哋應轉型學對家打選戰！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟愚昧，對選舉其實只有膚淺嘅知識，求連登智慧，我哋必須用盡所有方法去救手足！唔要再有人受傷被捕！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">對準政權弱點，<br />\n提防分化，<br />\n唔好話區選無用，<br />\n一定有影響佢先咁驚要出緊急法！！！<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999, 但推戰略post 喇！<br />\n集思廣益！！！<br />\n不分化！咩方法都要試 ！！<br />\n 記得唔好俾 mon post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分化到！！！<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0af1ab7c20114151c0be89667f97fced839affb0","tid":1631964,"uid":287844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:52.000Z","msg":"p 牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e169d3164027736d1a1b30597aac5ab058e31ebf","tid":1631964,"uid":287844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:44:32.000Z","msg":"係咪巳經沉底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好驚大家忽略咗選戰 ，<br />\n對家而家巳經駛橫手，姐係好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f48b3a531ab7d4e4533a16bdc5203b9b8a0dff5","tid":1631964,"uid":287844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:15.000Z","msg":"有冇 非p牌手足幫手出post，到時做唔切文宣喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a7a01456294bfb26737161fdddd45e53ed19abd","tid":1631964,"uid":95401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85c0bfc031a1855cb8948ec1f7560e4f8a7f1cb1","tid":1631964,"uid":95401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:12:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df1433fdecfabb00a8b8bd633792626013186db7","tid":1631964,"uid":95401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:25:46.000Z","msg":"推，重要post就無人理， 分化風向post就霸住熱門。"},{"pid":"fd12ba7d7a1ed5c272644a27c4cfae94c6879b7c","tid":1631964,"uid":21486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:40:48.000Z","msg":"[區選] 每日更新，18 區所有候選人提名<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eijczS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eijczS</a><br />\n<br />\n睇下入面兩個網<br />\n第一二點都cover左 （第一點做左一半）<br />\n第三點可以傾下點做"},{"pid":"1371c559afb4d45ad3152b14b62be83998c7319c","tid":1631964,"uid":256505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:56:55.000Z","msg":"p 牌推唔到　都要推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d8e0b96ed653d4989751c53085d515222475da","tid":1631964,"uid":287844,"like":0,"dislike":